headline: Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG) Upgraded by Mizuho as Insurance Brokerage Outlook Improves
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) is included among the 13 Best Income Stocks with Highest Upside Potential. On February 27, Mizuho upgraded Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) to Outperform from Neutral. It set a price target of $260, down from $277. The firm made the change after adjusting ratings across the insurance property […]
